::Feline::

She walked past the bridge and hummed to herself as she went alone.  
She dropped a few computer boards.  They hit the floor with a clang.  
She winced as the noise hurt her ears.  She sighed and tried to pick 
them up.  As she bent down to pick up a board, she dropped another 
board, it fell with a clang.  She tried to pick up another and 
dropped an arm on the floor with a bang.  This just wasn't her day.
